  |===                                                                          |   3%
| In this lesson, we'll review basic ideas of probability, the study of quantifying
| the likelihood of particular events occurring. Note the similarity between the words
| probability and probably. Every time you use the latter word you're implying that an
| event is more likely than not to occur.

...

